- [KV Cache Optimization: Memory Efficiency for Production LLMs](https://introl.com/blog/kv-cache-optimization-memory-efficiency-production-llms-guide) — PagedAttention、cache 命中率與成本的關係
- [Context Engineering for AI Agents: Lessons from Building Manus](https://manus.im/blog/context-engineering-for-ai-agents) — 原始出處：穩定前綴、避免時間戳破壞 cache、確定性序列化

**Memory Architecture**
- [Agent Engineering: IMPACT Framework](https://www.morphllm.com/agent-engineering) — Memory 作為 agent 六維度之一（Intent、Memory、Planning、Authority、Control Flow、Tools）
- [Agentic workflows for software development - McKinsey QuantumBlack](https://medium.com/quantumblack/agentic-workflows-for-software-development-dc8e64f4a79d) — Eval 在 artifact（file）上執行，不在對話回應上
- [Why AI Agents Fail: 3 Failure Modes - AWS DEV Community](https://dev.to/aws/why-ai-agents-fail-3-failure-modes-that-cost-you-tokens-and-time-1flb) — Memory Pointer Pattern（200KB → 100 bytes），context window overflow 的解法
